le.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160609/19647230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160609%2F19647230&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a5fd308c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160609%2F19647230&h=80a5f6be\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160609/19647230</a>"},{"pid":"b6fd0e7971c613e9ac36bd67aa33e8586c1803f6","tid":171292,"uid":10216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"IQ 高剩係令到香港人返工效率高，讀書背野勁，但其他野一樣咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e20d3d1e1d7d1789402820deb8619c20936564e","tid":171292,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解會咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實上，<span style=\"color: red;\">分析力， 視野， 邏輯都有問題</span><br />\n求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點會iq 高？</blockquote><br />\n我就係問緊<br />\nIQ應該包含依幾樣野， 如果依幾項都低， 香港人既IQ點解會咁高？</blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以視野同分析力而言，以history同中史啲essay同case study作例，只要睇多兩份範文同model answer，我哋就知essay format、答題技巧、考官想見到乜觀點同史例。只要見到相似topic，我哋都已經有個concept應對。但如果你貿貿然畀啲新嘢香港人，喺冇睇過model answer情況下叫佢分析，佢哋未必做到critical thinking同援引到好嘅例子去闡述<br />\n所以我認為香港人應該係學習能力高同應變力高，最後得出IQ高嘅結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於邏輯，香港人係強，但只限用於學業上，啫係考試同maths。如果你問佢哋點解薯片撐23條你都撐佢，佢又答唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以你從日常生活觀察香港人iq同用IQ test測香港人iq會得出唔同結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申9up"},{"pid":"8ea8d8e9ba15918aa567592a5b6f21a0e99fef64","tid":171292,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解會咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實上，<span style=\"color: red;\">分析力， 視野， 邏輯都有問題</span><br />\n求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點會iq 高？</blockquote><br />\n我就係問緊<br />\nIQ應該包含依幾樣野， 如果依幾項都低， 香港人既IQ點解會咁高？</blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以視野同分析力而言，以history同中史啲essay同case study作例，只要睇多兩份範文同model answer，我哋就知essay format、答題技巧、考官想見到乜觀點同史例。只要見到相似topic，我哋都已經有個concept應對。但如果你貿貿然畀啲新嘢香港人，喺冇睇過model answer情況下叫佢分析，佢哋未必做到critical thinking同援引到好嘅例子去闡述<br />\n所以我認為香港人應該係學習能力高同應變力高，最後得出IQ高嘅結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於邏輯，香港人係強，但只限用於學業上，啫係考試同maths。如果你問佢哋點解薯片撐23條你都撐佢，佢又答唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以你從日常生活觀察香港人iq同用IQ test測香港人iq會得出唔同結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申9up</blockquote><br />\n我都係9up, 一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有睇過IQ係用咩野成份黎計出黎<br />\n教育, 學術佔既比重最多, 所以香港人既IQ只係勁係某D領域<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係到critical thinking就出事"},{"pid":"dd4d79fcca087f5e5e9795fbd89ff4f1ad60c8a3","tid":171292,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"iq高有鬼用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da843d9a83c0de0852366e9592e8165392075e2d","tid":171292,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解會咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實上，<span style=\"color: red;\">分析力， 視野， 邏輯都有問題</span><br />\n求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點會iq 高？</blockquote><br />\n我就係問緊<br />\nIQ應該包含依幾樣野， 如果依幾項都低， 香港人既IQ點解會咁高？</blockquote><br />\n邊個話你聽香港人iq高？</blockquote><br />\n全球智商排名　港人稱冠<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160609/19647230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160609%2F19647230&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a5fd308c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160609%2F19647230&h=80a5f6be\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160609/19647230</a></blockquote><br />\n呢d 排名日日出百幾個，你睇樓價第一就已經知，度度都話自己最貴"}]}